<paragraph id="3D7B160BDE6FFF9AD6E4F923FD8E98AE" blockId="10.[166,1224,1676,1831]" pageId="10" pageNumber="213">
Epigyne as in 
<figureCitation id="A5FF0A8EDE6FFF9AD745F923FE2B98CE" box="[378,449,1676,1703]" captionStart="Figs 40–51" captionStartId="9.[174,213,1747,1769]" captionTargetBox="[189,1210,673,1697]" captionTargetId="figure-133@9.[189,1210,673,1697]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="Figs 40–51. Epigynes of Nediphya hippai sp. n. (40–41, 46, 49), N. padillai sp. n. (42), N. lehtineni (43, 50–51), N. lyleae sp. n. (44–45, 48) and Diphya macrophthalma (47). Scale = 0.2 mm. Abbreviations: Cd copulatory ducts, Er elongate anterior receptacles, Mp median plate, Re round proper receptacles, Rr round anterior receptacles." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6454201" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6454201/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="213">fig. 42</figureCitation>
; median plate 3 times wider than long, copulatory ducts “)(” shaped, separated by more than one diameter.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3D7B160BDE6FFF9AD6E4F963FE7F988E" blockId="10.[166,1224,1676,1831]" box="[219,405,1740,1767]" pageId="10" pageNumber="213">Male unknown.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3D7B160BDE6FFF9AD6E4F943FE5F994E" blockId="10.[166,1224,1676,1831]" pageId="10" pageNumber="213">
Distribution. The new species is known only from the 
<typeStatus id="E27FA8A9DE6FFF9AD5BFF943FC58996E" box="[896,946,1772,1799]" pageId="10" pageNumber="213">type</typeStatus>
locality where 
<taxonomicName id="FAC46D88DE6FFF9AD25BF942FB22996F" authorityName="Marusik &amp; Omelko" authorityYear="2017" box="[1124,1224,1772,1798]" class="Arachnida" family="Tetragnathidae" genus="Nediphya" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="213" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lyleae">
<emphasis id="0FB0CA19DE6FFF9AD25BF942FB22996F" box="[1124,1224,1772,1798]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="213">N. lyleae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is also known to occur.
</paragraph>
<caption id="69BB4683DE6EFF9BD686FD86FD3D9C56" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6454203" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6454203" box="[185,727,553,575]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6454203/files/figure.png" pageId="11" pageNumber="214" startId="11.[185,224,553,575]" targetBox="[212,1231,174,532]" targetPageId="11">
